staticFields.label: GetPopups
staticFields.description: Returns a list of all popups

staticMethods.label: SetLabel
staticMethods.description: Sets the label at a certain location. Valid types: "TopCenter", "TopLeft", "TopRight", "MiddleCenter", "MiddleLeft", "MiddleRight", "BottomLeft", "BottomRight", "BottomCenter".

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label location.

parameters.name: message
parameters.description: The message to display.

staticMethods.label: SetLabelForTime
staticMethods.description: Sets the label for a certain time, after which it will be cleared.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label location.

parameters.name: message
parameters.description: The message to display.

parameters.name: time
parameters.description: The time in seconds before the label is cleared.

staticMethods.label: SetLabelAll
staticMethods.description: Sets the label for all players. Master client only. Be careful not to call this often.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label location.

parameters.name: message
parameters.description: The message to display.

staticMethods.label: SetLabelForTimeAll
staticMethods.description: Sets the label for all players for a certain time. Master client only.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label location.

parameters.name: message
parameters.description: The message to display.

parameters.name: time
parameters.description: The time in seconds before the label is cleared.

staticMethods.label: CreatePopup
staticMethods.description: Creates a new popup. This popup is hidden until shown.

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup.

parameters.name: title
parameters.description: The title of the popup.

parameters.name: width
parameters.description: The width of the popup.

parameters.name: height
parameters.description: The height of the popup.

staticMethods.label: ShowPopup
staticMethods.description: Shows the popup with given name.

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup to show.

staticMethods.label: HidePopup
staticMethods.description: Hides the popup with given name.

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup to hide.

staticMethods.label: ClearPopup
staticMethods.description: Clears all elements in popup with given name.

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup to clear.

staticMethods.label: AddPopupLabel
staticMethods.description: Adds a text row to the popup with label as content.

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label text to add.

staticMethods.label: AddPopupButton
staticMethods.description: Adds a button row to the popup with given button name and display text. When button is pressed, OnButtonClick is called in Main with buttonName parameter.

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The button display text.

parameters.name: callback
parameters.description: The callback name that will be passed to OnButtonClick in Main.

staticMethods.label: AddPopupBottomButton
staticMethods.description: Adds a button to the bottom bar of the popup.

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The button display text.

parameters.name: callback
parameters.description: The callback name that will be passed to OnButtonClick in Main.

staticMethods.label: AddPopupButtons
staticMethods.description: Adds a list of buttons in a row to the popup.

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup.

parameters.name: labels
parameters.description: List of button display texts.

parameters.name: callbacks
parameters.description: List of callback names that will be passed to OnButtonClick in Main.

staticMethods.label: WrapStyleTag
staticMethods.description: Returns a wrapped string given style and args.

parameters.name: text
parameters.description: The text to wrap.

parameters.name: style
parameters.description: The style tag name.

parameters.name: arg
parameters.description: Optional style argument.

staticMethods.label: ShowChangeCharacterMenu
staticMethods.description: Shows the change character menu if main character is Human.

staticMethods.label: SetScoreboardHeader
staticMethods.description: Sets the display of the scoreboard header (default "Kills / Deaths...")

parameters.name: header
parameters.description: The header text to display.

staticMethods.label: SetScoreboardProperty
staticMethods.description: Sets which Player custom property to read from to display on the scoreboard. If set to empty string, will use the default "Kills / Deaths..." display.

parameters.name: property
parameters.description: The property name to read from Player custom properties.

staticMethods.label: GetThemeColor
staticMethods.description: Gets the color of the specified item. See theme json for reference.

parameters.name: panel
parameters.description: The panel name.

parameters.name: category
parameters.description: The category name.

parameters.name: item
parameters.description: The item name.

staticMethods.label: IsPopupActive
staticMethods.description: Returns if the given popup is active

parameters.name: popupName
parameters.description: The name of the popup to check.

staticMethods.label: SetLabelActive
staticMethods.description: Sets whether a label is active or not.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label name.

parameters.name: active
parameters.description: Whether the label should be active.

staticMethods.label: SetKDRPanelActive
staticMethods.description: Sets whether the KDR panel (top-left) is active or not.

parameters.name: active
parameters.description: Whether the KDR panel should be active.

staticMethods.label: SetMinimapActive
staticMethods.description: Sets whether the minimap is active or not.

parameters.name: active
parameters.description: Whether the minimap should be active.

staticMethods.label: SetChatPanelActive
staticMethods.description: Sets whether the chat panel is active or not.

parameters.name: active
parameters.description: Whether the chat panel should be active.

staticMethods.label: SetFeedPanelActive
staticMethods.description: Sets whether the feed panel is active or not.

parameters.name: active
parameters.description: Whether the feed panel should be active.

staticMethods.label: SetBottomHUDActive
staticMethods.description: Sets whether the bottom HUD is active or not. This can only be used when the character is alive.

parameters.name: active
parameters.description: Whether the bottom HUD should be active.

staticMethods.label: GetRootVisualElement
staticMethods.description: Returns the root `VisualElement` which you can add other elements to. Returns: The root `VisualElement`

staticMethods.label: VisualElement
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `VisualElement`.

staticMethods.label: Button
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `Button` with optional text and click event.

parameters.name: text
parameters.description: The text that the button displays

parameters.name: clickEvent
parameters.description: The function that will be called when button is clicked

staticMethods.label: Label
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `Label` with optional text.

parameters.name: text
parameters.description: The text to be displayed

staticMethods.label: TextField
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `TextField` with optional label.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label text displayed next to the TextField (default: empty).

staticMethods.label: Toggle
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `Toggle` with optional label and value changed event.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label text displayed next to the toggle

parameters.name: valueChangedEvent
parameters.description: The function that will be called when toggle value changes

staticMethods.label: Slider
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `Slider` for floating-point values with optional range, tick interval, and value changed event. The slider will snap to values at multiples of the tick interval.

parameters.name: lowValue
parameters.description: The minimum value of the slider

parameters.name: highValue
parameters.description: The maximum value of the slider

parameters.name: tickInterval
parameters.description: The interval between allowed values. If 0, no snapping occurs. For example, 0.1 will snap to 0.0, 0.1, 0.2, etc.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label text displayed next to the slider

parameters.name: valueChangedEvent
parameters.description: The function that will be called when slider value changes

staticMethods.label: SliderInt
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `Slider` for integer values with optional range, tick interval, and value changed event. The slider will snap to values at multiples of the tick interval.

parameters.name: lowValue
parameters.description: The minimum value of the slider

parameters.name: highValue
parameters.description: The maximum value of the slider

parameters.name: tickInterval
parameters.description: The interval between allowed values. For example, 5 will snap to 0, 5, 10, 15, etc.

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label text displayed next to the slider

parameters.name: valueChangedEvent
parameters.description: The function that will be called when slider value changes

staticMethods.label: Dropdown
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `Dropdown` with a list of choices and optional label and value changed event.

parameters.name: choices
parameters.description: List of string options to display in the dropdown

parameters.name: defaultIndex
parameters.description: The index of the initially selected option (default: 0)

parameters.name: label
parameters.description: The label text displayed next to the dropdown

parameters.name: valueChangedEvent
parameters.description: The function that will be called when dropdown value changes

staticMethods.label: ProgressBar
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `ProgressBar` with optional range, title, and value changed event.

parameters.name: lowValue
parameters.description: The minimum value of the progress bar (default: 0)

parameters.name: highValue
parameters.description: The maximum value of the progress bar (default: 100)

parameters.name: title
parameters.description: The title text displayed on the progress bar

parameters.name: valueChangedEvent
parameters.description: The function that will be called when progress bar value changes

staticMethods.label: ScrollView
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `ScrollView` for scrollable content.

staticMethods.label: Icon
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `Icon` element for displaying images/icons.

parameters.name: iconPath
parameters.description: Path to the icon resource (e.g., "Icons/Game/BladeIcon")

staticMethods.label: Image
staticMethods.description: Creates a new `Image` element for displaying images/icons.

parameters.name: iconPath
parameters.description: Path to the icon resource (e.g., "Icons/Game/BladeIcon")
